title: Mailvox: 4 not 5
author: VD
content_html: The star was a typo, sorry about that. I haven’t had direct access to the administration site since WND was hacked and I didn’t even see the article until this morning, so I didn’t know there was a problem and even if I had there wasn’t anything I could do about it anyhow. I am no relation to Omar Bradley.
